{"tid":557100,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做野幾年，發覺有一種能力係管理層同基層員工嘅分界線","createTime":"2018-02-11T04:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T15:39:08.000Z","uid":120847,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e307eea2cd1868d4ff6020fda9b1ee39c6bb1f6e","tid":557100,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:58:44.000Z","msg":"出黎做野幾年<br />\n我觀察到無論啲老闆做野幾廢都好<br />\n佢地有一種能力係比基層員工強好多<br />\n講緊嘅就係面對質問時嘅應對能力<br />\n<br />\n據我觀察，無論啲老闆嘅辦事能力幾廢都好，每當開會時俾高層質問or俾人挑機時，都可以好快好圓滑咁回應，就算明明對件事冇乜暸解都會up到啲野出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而啲基層員工好多執行能力好強 但面對質問時可能轉數唔夠快 依依俄俄咁答唔出啲咩 俾人問多兩句就一額汗 <br />\n呢種人就算做野幾叻都永遠唔出得大場面 唔可以做一個組織/部門嘅代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67834a9b353761c44ef00db1f3432f8ad2bf39cd","tid":557100,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:02:17.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"9af84f7925ec23e009ad2c13f8125abdee010dcc","tid":557100,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6255535ba79bebf30b832dd61c91db8ed2c4395","tid":557100,"uid":33257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"好同意  我應該點樣訓練自己好呢"},{"pid":"df3b4ed613f1d3f8e427bc6d9dc5da6bbb2d359a","tid":557100,"uid":120847,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6255535ba79bebf30b832dd61c91db8ed2c4395","tid":557100,"uid":33257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:18:43.000Z","msg":"好同意  我應該點樣訓練自己好呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"轉數可能係天生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d0b55b481d65fa5996fd97ba2aad7ca99e52d6","tid":557100,"uid":120847,"like":